resources.string: "Lovely and even seductive, enjoy authentic beachfront dining in open-air, thatched roof huts. Surrounded by tropical flowers with the alluring scent of jasmine filling the air, day into night, our restaurant is the ideal setting to savor the distinctive flavors of the Caribbean. Reservations are required",
